              "content": "Shipping & Deliveries\nDelivery Scope & Lead Times\nDelivery Scope: We only accept international orders. We do not offer delivery within Taiwan.\nDispatch Time: All orders are generally dispatched within 1-3 business days, unless otherwise stated.\nShipping Terms (DAP): All international orders are shipped under DAP (Delivered At Place) terms. Wish Liquor is responsible for the delivery of the goods to your specified address; however, the buyer is responsible for all import clearance, local taxes, and customs duties incurred in the destination country.\nMarketplace & Partner Retailers Some products are shipped directly from our partner retailers.\nShipping Policies: Specific shipping policies are displayed under the \"Add to Cart\" button on each product page.\nSeparate Charges: Orders shipped from different retailers may incur separate shipping charges.\nPre-Sales & Exclusive Releases For pre-sale events or exclusive bottlings, estimated dispatch dates will be clearly stated on the product page.\nFAQs\nWhere do we deliver? We deliver to most residential or business addresses. If your country is not listed at checkout, please contact us at wishliquor@outlook.com for a quote.\nHow much is the fee and how long does it take? Total delivery costs and estimated times depend on your location and weight, and will be displayed at checkout.\nHow do I track my order? You will receive a tracking number and an email notification once your order is dispatched.\nWill I have to sign for my delivery? Yes, a signature is required upon delivery. Persons ordering alcoholic beverages must be over the legal drinking age in their respective jurisdiction.\nContact Us For any inquiries, please contact us at: wishliquor@outlook.com",
